Description:
You arrive at the main Sahti settlement, but there are fewer people on the streets than you expected.

An elder greets you and explains the situation. It seems that a plague has struck most of the people, and they are short on the seaweed they use to treat it.

He would be very grateful if you could help the village by retrieving more of this seaweed.
DescriptionAction: Would you like to help the Sahti?
